CreatePrivateDNSAccount.document: This API is used to create a Private DNS account.
CreatePrivateDNSAccount.name: Creates Private DNS account

CreatePrivateZone.document: This API is used to create a private domain.
CreatePrivateZone.name: Creates private domain

CreatePrivateZoneRecord.document: This API is used to add a DNS record for a private domain.
CreatePrivateZoneRecord.name: Adds DNS record for private domain

DeletePrivateDNSAccount.document: This API is used to delete a Private DNS account.
DeletePrivateDNSAccount.name: Deletes Private DNS account

DeletePrivateZone.document: This API is used to delete a private domain and stop DNS.
DeletePrivateZone.name: Deletes private domain

DeletePrivateZoneRecord.document: This API is used to delete a DNS record for a private domain.
DeletePrivateZoneRecord.name: Deletes DNS record for private domain

DescribeAccountVpcList.document: This API is used to get the VPC list of a Private DNS account.
DescribeAccountVpcList.name: Gets the VPC list of a Private DNS account

DescribeAuditLog.document: This API is used to get the list of operation logs.
DescribeAuditLog.name: Gets the list of operation logs

DescribeDashboard.document: This API is used to get the overview of private DNS records.
DescribeDashboard.name: Gets the overview of private DNS records

DescribePrivateDNSAccountList.document: This API is used to get the list of Private DNS accounts.
DescribePrivateDNSAccountList.name: Gets the list of Private DNS accounts

DescribePrivateZone.document: This API is used to get the private domain information.
DescribePrivateZone.name: Gets private domain information

DescribePrivateZoneList.document: This API is used to get the list of private domains.
DescribePrivateZoneList.name: Gets the list of private domains

DescribePrivateZoneRecordList.document: This API is used to get the list of records for a private domain.
DescribePrivateZoneRecordList.name: Gets the list of records for private domain

DescribePrivateZoneService.document: This API is used to query the Private DNS activation status.
DescribePrivateZoneService.name: Queries Private DNS activation status

DescribeRequestData.document: This API is used to get the DNS request volume of a private domain.
DescribeRequestData.name: Gets the DNS request volume of private domain

ModifyPrivateZone.document: This API is used to modify a private domain.
ModifyPrivateZone.name: Modifies private domain

ModifyPrivateZoneRecord.document: This API is used to modify a DNS record for a private domain.
ModifyPrivateZoneRecord.name: Modifies DNS record for private domain

ModifyPrivateZoneVpc.document: This API is used to modify the VPC associated with a private domain.
ModifyPrivateZoneVpc.name: Modifies VPC associated with private domain

SubscribePrivateZoneService.document: This API is used to activate the Private DNS service.
SubscribePrivateZoneService.name: Activates Private DNS service
